---
import profile from '../data/profile';
---

<section id="contact" class="section-container text-center">
  <p class="text-accent font-mono text-sm mb-2 slide-up">05.</p>
  <h2 class="section-title mx-auto slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">Get In Touch</h2>
  <p class="section-subtitle slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">연락처</p>

  <p class="text-dark-muted leading-relaxed max-w-lg mx-auto mb-8 slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
    새로운 기회나 협업에 대해 이야기 나누고 싶으시다면 편하게 연락해 주세요. 최대한 빠르게 답변 드리겠습니다.
  </p>

  <div class="slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
    <a
      href={`mailto:${profile.email}`}
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent hover:bg-accent-hover text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-xl transition-colors"
    >
      <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21.75 6.75v10.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25 2.25h-15a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25-2.25V6.75m19.5 0A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 19.5 4.5h-15a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25 2.25m19.5 0v.243a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-1.07 1.916l-7.5 4.615a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.36 0L3.32 8.91a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-1.07-1.916V6.75" />
      </svg>
      이메일 보내기
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
